title: BigFish Games - Build-a-lot 3 - Passport to Europe - New Tycoon
description:
Build-a-lot 3 - Passport to Europe v1.0 FINAL Tycoon

Build-a-lot 3 is your passport to fun! Travel all over Europe as you 

restore rundown houses, develop friendly services and beautify 

neighborhoods with picturesque landmarks. The changing needs of the 

neighborhood will sure keep you busy--you may need to brave the rain 

and snow, deal with noisy neighbors, or even put out a small fire to 

get the job done on time! Pack your bags and let the fun take flight in 

the exciting sequel to Build-a-lot 1 & 2!


Restore rundown houses for big profits
Paint and landscape houses to increase curb appeal
Build picturesque landmarks to beautify neighborhoods
Construct friendly service buildings
Improve a neighborhood at your own pace in Casual mode

Thanx to TAC-CM
